Use Scanning to find and underline :
• Capitalised words (names and places)
• Numbers
• Terms explained in more detail using brackets
• Words that are in quotation marks

Skimming : Quickly getting the 'ging' of the text

Scanning : Quickly finding specific information

Basic Idea
• 4-5 min to read question and mark main point from it
• Read throughout and try to recognise deatil related to question
• Find answer as per required words
• In mcq, first eliminate wrong options
• In heading, find suitable list of heading and then think about each's possibility
• In True False Not given, find related all info and then select what to do
